measurements.description: Three flowers well presented on one 25-cm staked inflorescence; dorsal sepal cupuliform, rose-pink, spotted darker rose pink veins, darker rose-pink abaxial surface, spur 2.0 cm rose-pink; lateral sepals ovate, cupped, bright rose-pink; petals erect, cymbiform, oblong, yellow, maculated burgundy adabxial surface, rose-pink adaxial surface; lip narrowly lanceolate, recurved apically, rose-pink; column light rose-pink, anthers white; substance firm; texture satin.
